headline.main: SOVIET ISSUES DATA ON VOSKHOD FLIGHT

results.snippet: MOSCOW, Sept. 19 -- The Soviet Union pinpointed today for the first time the isolated spot in the snowbound northern forest where its last manned space vehicle, Voskhod-2, reached earth last March.
